OL,3,CAll patients moved out of Knoll
OL,4,CHospital, Duns, after RAAC found
OL,6,FAll patients have now been temporarily
OL,7,Fmoved from Knoll Community Hospital in
OL,8,FDuns, according to NHS Borders.
OL,10,FThey were relocated after Reinforced
OL,11,FAutoclaved Aerated Concrete (RAAC) was
OL,12,Ffound on the site in January.
OL,14,FThe health board said: "Staff from NHS
OL,15,FBorders, affected GP Practices and the
OL,16,Fwider Health and Social Care
OL,17,FPartnership continue to work round the
OL,18,Fclock to progress the safe relocation
OL,19,Fof patients and services from the
OL,20,FKnoll Hospital site."
