OL,3,CAll patients moved out of Knoll
OL,4,CHospital, Duns, after RAAC found
OL,6,FNHS Borders has already found new
OL,7,Fsites for most services, with work
OL,8,F"underway to schedule moves."
OL,10,FSome services have been able to move
OL,11,Fto different parts of the community
OL,12,Fhospital site unaffected by RAAC.
OL,14,FImpacted patients will be contacted
OL,15,Fdirectly about where to go for
OL,16,Ftreatment that would have been
OL,17,Fprovided at the health centre. Further
OL,18,Fdetails are said to be being provided
OL,19,Fnext week to advise the public of
OL,20,Fthese arrangements.
